  "text": "Oligoclonal T cell receptors that proliferate in culture with enterocytes and are cytotoxic to enterocyte cell lines were reported in PSC but this study is unconfirmed [CITATION_1] . There are to date no studies of regulatory T cells (T regs) in PSC patients.",
